description: Variation of Condition 2 (Approved Drawings) of planning permission 0141/09: Consisting of: Additional 22 residential units; Removal of D1 (non-residential institutions) and D2 (assembly and leisrue) or live/work units; Replacement of basement parking with undercroft parking at grade (providing 117 parking spaces); An additional storey on Block C and an additional of part-2 storeys on Block B; An additional storey on the inner faade of block A; Removal of live-works units; 2 private podium deck courtyards between Block A-B and B-C including an additional under-5s play area.
